<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293887" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/jinri-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-12-01/doc-iiznezxs4702610.shtml">嫦娥五号成功落月</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383215" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9c942f537eba4e229671e74f32213161.jpg" alt="" width="1000" height="667" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9c942f537eba4e229671e74f32213161.jpg 1000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9c942f537eba4e229671e74f32213161-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9c942f537eba4e229671e74f32213161-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /></p>
<p>昨晚 23 时 11 分，嫦娥五号探测器成功着陆在月球正面西经 51.8 度、北纬 43.1 度附近的预选着陆区，并传回着陆影像图。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383217" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/hjkhkj.jpeg" alt="" width="800" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/hjkhkj.jpeg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/hjkhkj-360x360.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/hjkhkj-768x768.jpeg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 嫦娥五号软着陆后降落相机拍摄的图像</p>
</div>
<p>嫦娥五号探测器成为我国第三个成功实施月面软着陆的探测器。成功着陆后，着陆器在地面控制下，将正式开始持续约 2 天的月面工作。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1060567.htm">高通发布骁龙 888</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383218" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/493eb750-3396-11eb-b7fd-4ebdea1ef922.jpeg" alt="" width="1600" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/493eb750-3396-11eb-b7fd-4ebdea1ef922.jpeg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/493eb750-3396-11eb-b7fd-4ebdea1ef922-360x225.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/493eb750-3396-11eb-b7fd-4ebdea1ef922-768x480.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/493eb750-3396-11eb-b7fd-4ebdea1ef922-1024x640.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>高通正式发布了骁龙 888。骁龙 888 采用了 5nm 制程工艺，集成高通第三代 5G 调制解调器及射频系统，支持全球毫米波和 Sub-6GHz 全部主要频段，以及 5G 载波聚合、全球多 SIM 卡功能、独立（SA）和非独立（NSA）组网模式以及动态频谱共享（DSS），是面向全球的兼容性 5G 平台。</p>
<p>小米宣布，小米 11 将全球首发骁龙 888 移动平台。OPPO 宣布全新一代 Find X 系列手机将搭载骁龙 888 移动平台，具体发布时间为明年第一季度。</p>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/tACKFvQj5mgLQERZOCIzLw">IDC：智能手表成可穿戴设备主力</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383220" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/QQ20190412-152940.jpg" alt="" width="1678" height="840" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/QQ20190412-152940.jpg 1678w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/QQ20190412-152940-360x180.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/QQ20190412-152940-768x384.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/QQ20190412-152940-1024x513.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1678px) 100vw, 1678px" /></p>
<p>IDC 数据显示，2020 年第三季度，成人手表市场出货量 450 万台，同比增长 76.8%，创下近一年来增速新高。其中基础手表在华为的带领下，众多厂商积极跟进，共同促进其市场出货量增速达到 138.8%；智能手表市场在 Apple Watch 的新品带动下恢复增长，同比实现 25.5% 的增速。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383221" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/640.png" alt="" width="878" height="383" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/640.png 878w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/640-360x157.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/640-768x335.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 878px) 100vw, 878px" /></p>
<p>IDC 研究经理认为，「成人手表市场已经发展成为可穿戴设备中的重要组成部分，并且成为未来消费 IoT 生态布局上的重要一环。成人手表与各场景的入口设备的联动，不仅提升了手表的应用价值，更加提升了其他智能设备对于用户需求的识别和判断能力。」</p>
